com.solacesystems.jndi  

Online developer documentation for JMS 1.1 API and the Solace JMS implementation.

This online Help application describes JMS classes, interfaces, constructors, methods, and fields. It does not provide an overview of the Solace JMS implementation, nor does it provide overviews or procedures for performing common messaging tasks. It is recommended that you read the Solace Messaging API for JMS - User Guide to familiarize yourself with how to create new or integrate existing Java applications using JMS for use with the Solace Messaging Platform.
